        "subject": "DDN-151 server: add health_check routine to the MDS and MGS",
        "message": "DDN-151 server: add health_check routine to the MDS and MGS\n\nPatch adds obd_health_check() methods in MDS and MGS to check\nptlrpc services health like OST does. Patch adds also health_check()\nroutine directly to OSD to check it is mounted and not read-only.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Id5c2093e8fa8fd1acf4ca370db9f2d139f8661d3\n"
